              <div class="faq-a" role="region">High Tide Radar is our exclusive audience intelligence platform. It identifies anonymous website visitors and matches them against 200M+ verified consumer and business profiles built from 300+ behavioral, demographic, and intent attributes. We use that information to make sure every dollar you spend on marketing only reaches people who are actually in the market for your services.</div>
