              </button>
              <div class="faq-a" role="region">Yes. For B2B clients, Radar identifies which companies are researching your services, what competitors they are visiting, and where they are in the buying process. For B2C, we match in-market consumers based on behavior, intent, and life stage. The approach is the same. The data is tailored to your market.</div>
